function startbutton()

function playerbutton(numberOfPlayers_)

end

function creditsbutton()
    hideAll();
    self.UI.show("creditsmenu")
end

function mainmenu()
    hideAll();
    self.UI.show("startmenu")
end

function hideAll()
    self.UI.hide("playermenu")

end

<!-- https://api.tabletopsimulator.com/ui/introUI/ -->

<VerticalLayout id="startmenu" padding="200 200 0 100">
    <Image image="logo" />
    <Button onClick="startbutton">
        <Text fontSize="50">Start Game</Text>
    </Button>
    <Button onClick="creditsbutton">
        <Text fontSize="50">Credits</Text>
    </Button>
    <Button>
        <Text fontSize="50">Tutorial</Text>
    </Button>
</VerticalLayout>

<VerticalLayout id="creditsmenu" padding="0 0 0 0">
    <Image image="innlogo" />
    <Text fontSize="75" color="#FFFFFF">Herman Ibsen Aursø</Text>
    <Text fontSize="75" color="#FFFFFF">Celina Gammelsæter</Text>
    <Text fontSize="75" color="#FFFFFF">Thomas Carlsen</Text>

    <Button onClick="mainmenu">
        <Text fontSize="50">Back</Text>
    </Button>
</VerticalLayout>

<VerticalLayout id="playermenu">
    <Text fontSize="50" color="#FFFFFF">Select number of players</Text>
    <Button onClick="playerbutton(6)">
        <Text fontSize="50">Six Players</Text>
    </Button>
    <Button onClick="playerbutton(5)">
        <Text fontSize="50">Five Players</Text>
    </Button>
    <Button onClick="playerbutton(4)">
        <Text fontSize="50">Four Players</Text>
    </Button>
    <Button onClick="playerbutton(3)">
        <Text fontSize="50">Three Players</Text>
    </Button>
    <Button onClick="playerbutton(2)">
        <Text fontSize="50">Two Players</Text>
    </Button>
</VerticalLayout>
